- reset_tokens: id, user_id, token, expires_at, used
- payments: id, inquiry_id, amount, status, external_reference, created_at
- sessions: id, user_id, access_token, refresh_token, expires_at

API Endpoints: [Routes and methods]
- POST /api/auth/register
- POST /api/auth/login
- POST /api/auth/logout
- POST /api/auth/resend-verification
