- PATCH /api/inquiries/:id
- POST /api/payments/confirm
- GET /api/payments/:id

Security: 
- Use bcrypt/argon2 for password hashing
- Use JWTs or secure cookies with HttpOnly, Secure flags
- Tokens for email verification and password reset with expiry
- Role-based access control via middleware (guest/host/concierge)
- Rate limiting on verification/resend and password reset endpoints
- Validation on all inputs; sanitize outputs
- Do not expose sensitive data in responses

Validation: 
- Email format check, password strength rules
- Required fields for signup, listing creation, inquiry submission
- Dates and guests count validations
- Normalize responses: const data = response?.data ?? [] or verify Array.isArray patterns

Acceptance Criteria

